          "display_name": null,
          "email": "jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org",
          "username": "jwagantall"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-09-12 18:09:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+2\n\nIn this case in particular, many fixes/changes are happening in self releases. We want to make sure LF carefully upgrades global jjb to prevent 1/2 fixes going through. \nIn this case this change should be good to go as the current self release changes are tested and safe.",
        "patchset_number": 2
